    <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <span>Join the Stairway Team</span>
  </nav>
  <header class="container-prose ft-header">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-blue mb-4">Stairway</span>
    <h1 class="display-md">Join the Stairway Team</h1>
  </header>
  <article class="container-prose prose-editorial ft-body" set:html={`<h1>A High-Performance Culture for Ambitious Professionals
</h1>				
		<p><br />At Stairway Mortgage, we don’t just hire—we grow leaders. Our team is made up of driven, goal-oriented people who thrive under pressure and overcome challenges with grit. We value character, accountability, and discipline over experience—skills can be taught. If you’re committed to growth and excellence, you’ll feel right at home.</p>		
					<h2>Two Roads. One Destination: Success.</h2>				
									<h3>
							Sales-Oriented Professionals						
					</h3>
									<p>
						- Build relationships, network, and close deals<br>
- Thrive on challenge, persuasion, and performance<br>
- High risk, high reward—six-figure potential					</p>
			<a href="https://forms.stairwaymortgage.com/widget/survey/WGombd892PhSYF3yMwH9">
						</a>
									<h3>
							Operations-Oriented Professionals						
					</h3>
									<p>
						- System-focused, organized, detail-oriented<br>
- Enjoy consistency, precision, and behind-the-scenes mastery<br>
- Career security with strong income potential					</p>
			<a href="https://forms.stairwaymortgage.com/widget/survey/WGombd892PhSYF3yMwH9">
						</a>
															<img width="1024" height="1024" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Create-an-Image-on-Image_-Smiling-woman-on-a-video-call-at-home-with-coffee-and-laptop_Caption_-Freedom-focus-and-fulfillment—no-office-required.-Dont-use-any-text-in-image-1024x1024.jpg" alt="" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Create-an-Image-on-Image_-Smiling-woman-on-a-video-call-at-home-with-coffee-and-laptop_Caption_-Freedom-focus-and-fulfillment—no-office-required.-Dont-use-any-text-in-image-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Create-an-Image-on-Image_-Smiling-woman-on-a-video-call-at-home-with-coffee-and-laptop_Caption_-Freedom-focus-and-fulfillment—no-office-required.-Dont-use-any-text-in-image-300x300.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Create-an-Image-on-Image_-Smiling-woman-on-a-video-call-at-home-with-coffee-and-laptop_Caption_-Freedom-focus-and-fulfillment—no-office-required.-Dont-use-any-text-in-image-150x150.jpg 150w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Create-an-Image-on-Image_-Smiling-woman-on-a-video-call-at-home-with-coffee-and-laptop_Caption_-Freedom-focus-and-fulfillment—no-office-required.-Dont-use-any-text-in-image-768x768.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Create-an-Image-on-Image_-Smiling-woman-on-a-video-call-at-home-with-coffee-and-laptop_Caption_-Freedom-focus-and-fulfillment—no-office-required.-Dont-use-any-text-in-image-710x710.jpg 710w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Create-an-Image-on-Image_-Smiling-woman-on-a-video-call-at-home-with-coffee-and-laptop_Caption_-Freedom-focus-and-fulfillment—no-office-required.-Dont-use-any-text-in-image-600x600.jpg 600w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Create-an-Image-on-Image_-Smiling-woman-on-a-video-call-at-home-with-coffee-and-laptop_Caption_-Freedom-focus-and-fulfillment—no-office-required.-Dont-use-any-text-in-image.jpg 1120w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															
					<h2>Flexible &amp; Remote Work
Opportunities</h2>				
		<p>Whether you’re in the field or working from a café, we believe in results over hours.</p><ul><li>Work remotely and control your schedule</li><li>Collaborate in your city through networking and outreach</li><li>Focus on performance—not micromanagement</li></ul>		
					<h3>Why Join Stairway Mortgage?</h3>				
									<h3>
							Uncapped Earning Potential						
					</h3>
									<p>
						You control your income. With our competitive model, your success determines your paycheck—no caps, no limits.					</p>
									<h3>
							Elite-Level Training						
					</h3>
									<p>
						Access high-performance training that turns ambition into results. Learn from top producers and real-world experts. 					</p>
									<h3>
							Leadership Growth Paths						
					</h3>
									<p>
						Whether you’re new or seasoned, we offer defined tracks to help you grow into leadership roles and expand your influence. 					</p>
									<h3>
							Supportive Culture &amp; Flexibility						
					</h3>
									<p>
						Join a team that values collaboration, support, and the freedom to work from anywhere—with a community that’s always got your back.  					</p>
					<h2>Career Opportunities at Stairway Mortgage</h2>				
